                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This is the check I lost in my belt.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I took the things from the man when he was <hi rend="italic">lying</hi> drunk on the table; I intended to go to Portsmouth to see my friends, and return back and give them to him afterwards.</p>
